reviews.review_text:
great show, lousy sound, but better than the other source well,the title of this review says most of it
why listen to as much as you can  stand?
it is, like i say,  better than the other source, and,  man,  the audience is  so into the show,  at least  dig the clapping on the cumberland,  as the music  plays the  band,

Yeah-ehh-yeah First ever Donna PITB caterwaul at 12:14. Memorialized on DP30 as well. 

Five stars for great show, minus one for the introduction of the caterwaul, and minus two more for the absolutely horrid sound. Get DP 30.
